author: fmeschbe
msg: FELIX-2099 Cleanup loggging: All logging now goes through the GenericServlet.log methods where the AbstractWebConsolePlugin provides log methods taking a log level used to filter log messages on a log level configurable for all web console plugins. Removing the now unused Logger and BaseManagementPlugin classes. Simplifying the BasedUpdateInstallHelper and its extension classes using a SimpleWebConsolePlugin as its basis for logging and service access. Add configuration option (loglevel) to configure the loglevel message filter.
